ActBankruptcy and Insolvency Act
SubjectRules Amending the Bankruptcy and Insolvency General Rules (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRules Amending the BANKRUPTCY AND INSOLVENCY GENERAL RULES (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to repeal "Schedule, Part I, Tariff of Costs" from the Rules. Since subsection 197(5) of the Bankruptcy and Insolvency Act was repealed, the Schedule no longer has a practical relevance.
